<div id="overview" class="bg-white description">
	<div class="container">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-12">

				<h2>Adventurer! Speak the word of opening!</h2>

				<p>...Or, in other words, please enter the password for your personal Bundle of Holding account, which opens wide the doors of our site so you can get to <em>all</em> your <strong>Wizard's Cabinet</strong> download pages. (If you don't have an account yet, see below.) Under "Email," use the email address you used to buy your bundles.</p>
								<form name="login" action="/user/login" method="POST">
					<div class="row mb-3">
						<div class="col-md-6">
							<label class="form-label" for="users_email">Email:</label>
							<input class="form-control" type="email" name="users_email" autofocus id="users_email" value="team@irrgardless.com" data-lpignore="true">
						</div>
						<div class="col-md-6">
							<label class="form-label" for="password">Password:</label>
							<input class="form-control" type="password" name="password" id="password" value="">
						</div>
					</div>
					<div class="form-check mb-3">
						<input class="form-check-input" type="checkbox" name="remember" id="remember" value="1">
						<label for="remember" class="form-check-label">Remember me for a month</label> (Don't use this on a public computer!)					</div>

					<input type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" name="submit" value="Open the way!">
				</form>
				<p>
					<a href="/user/reset">I failed my Intelligence roll and forgot my password</a>
				</p>
			</div>
			<hr class="body_hr">
			<h3>No account?</h3>
<p>If you haven't yet purchased one of our offers, relax! You don't need to create an account. Your account gathers the files from all your past purchases in one location. If you haven't bought anything yet, there's nothing to gather.</p>		</div>
	</div>
</div>


